<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3556] Unneeded check in HA blob store configuration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3556</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The BlobServer in HA mode checks whether `ConfigConstants.STATE_BACKEND` has been configured, which is not needed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Remove the check and fail if recovery mode is ZooKeeper and no path has been configured.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12945807">FLINK-3556</key>
            <summary>Unneeded check in HA blob store configuration</summary>
